2025-10-30ISEDBudget Implementation Act, 2024, No. 1Order Fixing the Day on Which this Order Is Made as the Day on Which Division 37 of Part 4 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2024, No. 1 Comes into ForceOrder fixing the day on which this order is made as the day on which division 37 of part 4 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2024, No. 1 comes into force in order to modify the Telecommunications Act by including provisions which will empower consumers to make well-informed decisions around their telecommunications services by decreasing barriers to switching plans and providers.N/A
subject: Order Fixing the Day on Which this Order Is Made as the Day on Which Division 37 of Part 4 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2024, No. 1 Comes into Force
precis: Order fixing the day on which this order is made as the day on which division 37 of part 4 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2024, No. 1 comes into force in order to modify the Telecommunications Act by including provisions which will empower consumers to make well-informed decisions around their telecommunications services by decreasing barriers to switching plans and providers.
